These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
City: marseilles, venice
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, social-worker
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, fishing
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, green
1. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
2. the musician is on the right of the social-worker##1
3. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| City      | venice      | marseilles    |
| Job           | social-worker | musician |
| Hobby   | drawing       | fishing  |
| Color     | emerald      | green     |

