.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, r&b
House: craftsman, colonial
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, march
1. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Sport          | surfing | cycling |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | r&b         |
| House           | colonial     | craftsman         |
| Birthday     | march    | august    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, documentary
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, project-manager
City: hamburg, boston
2 different pets are kept: hamster, pony
1. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
4. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Movie-Genre         | documentary          | zombie |
| Job           | project-manager | analyst     |
| City   | hamburg            | boston         |
| Pet     | pony         | hamster   |

