.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, tea
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, rock-climbing
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, dahlia
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
2. the person drinking tea is the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | tea     | cola   |
| Transport   | boat    | snowmobile |
| Hobby   | writing   | rock-climbing |
| Flower           | orchid | dahlia    |

