3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
4. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | tea |
| Music-Genre   | punk     | funk      |
| House   | farmhouse | ranch-style   |
| Game         | billiard  | chess |

