.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, skydiving
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, amaryllis
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, march
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, taxi
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who growslily is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Hobby      | skydiving     | chess |
| Flower          | amaryllis   | lily |
| Birthday   | march     | february     |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi     |

 